definition.text: The data building procedure processes information to be fed to properties that are stored in the output dataset.

translations.text: El Data Building Procedure  procesa la información que se enviará a las propiedades que se almacenan en el conjunto de datos de salida.
Процедура построения данных обрабатывает информацию, которая должна быть передана свойствам, хранящимся на выход�� данных.

paragraphs.text: This procedure holds the core logic of the bot, as it features the code that performs the calculations required to produce the new data set. The code is split between a procedure initialization and a procedure loop.
